				<div class="container grid top-section">
                    <h1 class="article-title">A new study looks at ways to cut roadkill numbers for small and medium-sized mammals</h1>
                    	<div class="subtitle">Tr../../news.htmlpanded Highway 175 from Quebec City to the Saguenay has been a cause of death for thousands of small and medium-sized mammals </div>

                    <div class="clearfix"></div>

                    <div class="infos">
                        <div class="row-fluid stack-tablet-1 stack-mobile-1">
                            <div class="parsys_column span8">
                                    <div class="date">February 12, 2019</div>
                                    	<div class="separator">|</div>
                                    <div class="author">By 
    
                                        		<a href="http://www.concordia.ca/news/authors/patrick-lejtenyi.html">Patrick Lejtenyi</a>
                                	</div>
                            </div>
                            
                                <div class="parsys_column span4">
                                    <div class="social-media">
                                        


